node.text:
@LindseyHoran10 was one of Semahj’s favorite players on the @USWNT. Semahj won the SheBelives Hero™ contest, a contest that chooses a young person between the ages of 13-17 who embodies the SheBelieves spirit. Since meeting on FaceTime, they’ve developed an awesome friendship & Semahj has become like a little sister. Watch their touching story.
 
A SheBelieves Hero™ is a leader in their community, a confident and passionate individual who empowers others around them and works to make a difference.

node.title: Episode 4: Meeting Semahj, the SheBelieves Hero™

node.text:
Before the 2019 FIFA Women’s World Cup, @USWNT had a two week pre-camp in Tottenham where Lindsey & her teammate Morgan got locked into a bathroom at an alpaca farm. 😅 After freeing themselves, they met a not-so-cooperative Alfie the Alpaca. 😳 Let’s just say Lindsey is thankful that she’s a soccer player & not an alpaca handler. 😁

Get to know Lindsey & cheer her on as she gets ready to chase Tokyo Gold beginning July 21st at 1:30 a.m. PDT. #onaquest

node.title: When @LindseyHoran10 got Locked in an European Bathroom then Met Alfie 🦙

node.text:
A nervous & shy @lindseyhoran10, early in her professional soccer career, was called up to the @USWNT to play in the 2013 Algarve Cup in Portugal, an invitational tournament for national teams in women's association football hosted by the Portuguese Football Federation. Still unsure whether she belonged, an empowering message from a teammate gave her all the courage she needed. 📝🙌💪
 
Get to know Lindsey & cheer her on as she gets ready to chase Tokyo Gold beginning July 21st at 1:30 a.m. PDT. #onaquest

node.text: THE FULL LENGTH PANEL! Talking nutrition, mindset, & keeping active in 2021 with guests @goodybeats, @ericthetrainer, @janine_delaney, & @fuelwellwithkrissy. 💯  Hosts: @gracefulbygrace & @gisellecc.

Watch the inspirational story of our 2020 90 Day Challenge Winning Team - @NASM_Fitness Trainer Larry Ybarra, & his client + wife Marcia Ybarra. They receive a $20,000 grand prize to be split b/w them, a year supply of Quest goodies, & more!
•
We had unique circumstances in this challenge given the COVID-19 pandemic came upon us in the middle of it. Some of the unforeseen changes contestants faced included their gyms closing, limited to their homes, and no face-to-face time between trainer and client. Eighty nine (89) #NASM Certified Personal Trainers & client pairs made it to the final round at the end. WATCH @nasm_fitness Master Trainer @dragonmasterbri surprise the winning team that they won the $20,000 grand prize!

This is the third annual 90 Day Challenge hosted by Quest Nutrition x #NASM. Eighty nine (89) NASM Certified Personal Trainers & client pairs made it to the final round at the end! Finalists were selected by the NASM Master Instructors based on % of weight loss or gained relative to starting weight and overall body transformation. #onaquest #nasmcpt
